               <p>I am a <rs id="t17780429-62-viclabel293" type="occupation">publican</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17780429-62-victim571 t17780429-62-viclabel293"></join>; the prisoner was in my tap-room; she took a pot and went backwards; when she returned, I asked her for the pot; she denied she had any. She went out, I followed her and brought her back, and found the pot in her apron, and charged a constable with her.</p>

               <p>[The pot was produced in court, by the constable, and deposed to by the prosecutor.]</p>

               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>

               <p>I am not guilty. I did not take the pot.</p>

